{"tid":1782080,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國務院：美國將續漸取消關稅   侵：撚有，咪鳩噏","createTime":"2019-12-13T15:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T23:37:23.000Z","uid":26179,"like":475,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"927ef72c85a54fa6aebfec190015202ff18cca97","tid":1782080,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:51:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">國務院新聞辦罕見地在深夜11時召開記者會，商務部副部長王受文表示，中美達成首階段貿易協議，並表示美國將會分階段取消關稅，並且實現關稅，由升到降轉變。可是，在中方召開記者會的同時，美國總統特朗普在Twitter上表示，美國向中國產品徵收的25%關稅會保留，其餘徵收15%關稅的貨品，稅率則會減至7.5%。至於原來在本周日計劃加徵的新一輪關稅，就不會實施。特朗普又稱，中美將會開始磋第二階段的協議，相信這將會是十分美好的協議。</span><br />\n<br />\n好撚柒喎老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c8810f93a58728e07bae8dbd1fba99be5ade32","tid":1782080,"uid":263366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借一借個位<br />\n［行動post]入黎睇！一個真正經濟攬炒既平安夜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"26f77c44f1f811f4be15f966ed36e48c412901c6","tid":1782080,"uid":263406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借一借位宣傳<br />\n［行動post]入黎睇！一個真正經濟攬炒既平安夜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c4ff0f8cd7df361a0c12c2b3f15d0cb8b57661e0","tid":1782080,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7d933eff7b5ade3843832812a3cbd2e6e3696c","tid":1782080,"uid":127929,"like":13,"dislike":30,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"笑到我孛力走已口左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset